## 9. Configuration

### 9.1. Где хранить

- **Linux/macOS:** XDG Base Directory — `$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/<app>/config` (`~/.config/<app>/`)
- **Windows:** `%APPDATA%\<app>\config`
- **State / cache** — `$XDG_STATE_HOME` / `$XDG_CACHE_HOME` соответственно

### 9.2. Format

- **TOML** — modern recommend (cargo / gh / etc)
- **YAML** — popular but parsing gotchas
- **JSON** — machine-friendly, human-hostile
- **INI** — legacy but acceptable
- Match ecosystem expectations (Rust → TOML, Python → пешая TOML / YAML, и т.д.)

### 9.3. Hot reload

При изменении config — reload без restart (watch file, signal-driven). Опционально, но nice.

---

## 10. Logging + debugging

- **Logs to stderr** — не корраптить TUI stdout
- **Debug mode** (`DEBUG=1` или `--debug`) — extra verbose logging
- **Log file** — XDG state dir, не вперемешку с stdout
- **Никогда** не печатать debug в TUI canvas

---

## 11. Frameworks-first для TUI

| Framework | Language | Comment |
|---|---|---|
| **ratatui** (был `tui-rs`) | Rust | Modern, active, immediate-mode |
| **crossterm** | Rust | Terminal control layer; pairs with ratatui |
| **Textual** | Python | Modern, React-like, CSS-styled |
| **Rich** | Python | Output formatting (not TUI per se but adjacent) |
| **Bubble Tea** | Go | Elm-architecture inspired, popular |
| **Lipgloss** | Go | Styling layer pairs with Bubble Tea |
| **blessed** / **terminal-kit** | Node.js | Mature options |
| **ncurses** / **notcurses** | C | Old guard, low-level |
| **Charm libs** (Bubbles, Glamour) | Go | Higher-level components, beautiful |

### 11.1. Не пишем сами

| Категория | Готовое |
|---|---|
| Terminal capabilities detection | termcap / terminfo через library |
| Color palette management | library-built-in |
| Layout / box-drawing | library-built-in |
| Input handling (keyboard / mouse) | library-built-in |
| Resize handling | library-built-in |
| Async / event loop | language ecosystem (tokio / asyncio / etc) |

---

## 12. Compatibility matrix

Тестируем на:

- **Modern terminals:** Alacritty, Kitty, WezTerm, iTerm2 (macOS), Windows Terminal
- **Stock:** xterm, Terminal.app (macOS), GNOME Terminal, Konsole, PowerShell
- **Multiplexers:** tmux, GNU screen, Zellij
- **SSH:** через ssh tunnel — keybindings + colors работают

**ASCII fallback** обязателен — Unicode не везде доступен (старые systems / corporate locked-down environments).

---

## 13. TUI-specific checklist

В дополнение к `ui-style-guide-base.md` § 7:

- [ ] Adaptive layout — обрабатывает SIGWINCH (terminal resize)
- [ ] Color palette detection (256 / 24-bit / 16 / NO_COLOR)
- [ ] ASCII fallback (`--ascii` или `NO_UNICODE` env)
- [ ] Keybindings discoverable через `?` / F1
- [ ] Universal keys respected (q/Esc/Ctrl+C/Enter/Tab)
- [ ] Не передаём значение только цветом
- [ ] Spinner / progress respects `NO_ANIMATION`
- [ ] Status bar — single source of truth для state
- [ ] Logs to stderr / log file, не stdout
- [ ] Config в XDG Base Directory (Linux/macOS)
- [ ] UTF-8 + East Asian Width support
- [ ] Mouse support optional, keyboard primary
- [ ] Cancellable long ops (SIGINT graceful)
- [ ] Tested на ≥ 3 terminals + ≥ 1 multiplexer + SSH
